                           tone); red.</seg>
                        <date>Hand a: late 19th cent. Hand b, c: late 19 or early 20th cent.
                           (?)</date>
                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra; two initial lines in the incipit of
                           the texts; names of the kings; elements of Ethiopic numerals; elements of
                           the punctuation signs.</seg>
                     </handNote>
                     <handNote xml:id="h2" script="Ethiopic">Hand a (<locus from="3r" to="108r">3r-108r</locus>): small, rounded, broad spaced letters.
                        </handNote>
